The new UI is an improvement, but there are critical issues. Card linking fails with a "card info not found" error, and Touch ID remains unusable even when enabled. Accessing the balance requires an unnecessary four-step process. Additionally, users should be given the option to choose between PIN, biometric, or password login, with the flexibility to use biometrics alongside PIN and password for enhanced security.
